descriptionHtml:
Adds Sarah Jessica Parker to Skyrim near Anise's Cabin.

Load before Convenient Horse Herding by [b]Alek[/b]
(Loading after renders her useless if you use another horse)

Texture used in screenshot provided by Alienslof who kindly gave permission for texture use.

This mod will never be uploaded to steam workshop. Sarah will always be free to ride, otherwise it would be illegal everywhere but Nevada.

Sarah Jessica Parker is a truly under appreciated actress. She is very talented, and has the most expansive list of movies and tv shows, she's starred in than anyone else. She's been in Footloose, Sex and the City, and every western ever made.
author: Stalfos81
